name: TheAlly's Mix II: Churned
description:
I've updated my popular TheAlly's Mix! It still retains its' solid good-solid-all-round-general-purpose qualities, but now has an added bit of realism (using the token photo).

I've used the same sample images as my first mix, so you can go and compare how this stacks up against the OG.

It's a mix of Waifu Diffusion 1.3 and Stable Diffusion 1.5, with a further Sigmoid Interpolated NovelAI.


Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, prompt reveals, explanations, exclusive embeddings, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally

There are no trigger words required. The model "listens" to Danbooru tags, obeys prompts, and accepts Textual Inversions well!
